More to add to the topic:<P>As a continuation thought to the camo skill.. how do lions, cheetahs, pathers hunt their prey.  They sneak up undetected to where they are close enough to strike.  This falls directly inline with BST rollplaying.<P>NEW SKILL:  Speed. (mimics those animals like cheetahs to use high speeds)  This again is a clickable skill that at 2 skill point increases your speed by 1%.  You again skill points by using it starting it at level 1.  Limited to 5 points per level as most other skills.  I would allow this skill to cap at 230 in skill which means that at max, (45th level) his SELF speed would be increased by 115% percent for a duration of 30 seconds and reload every 10 minutes.
