Personally i feel that the skills that you outlined, however well they might fit into the roleplay aspect of the game, are ludicrously overpowering and are entirely impractical for the VI staff to adopt and transfer into a gameplay environment.<P>I feel that it is entirely unreasonable to expect any of these skills and would personally urge anyone from the VI staff *not* to use them, however unlikely it may seem that they would anyway.<P>Don't get your hopes up, boys.<P>--------------------<P>and that's all i have to say about that<P>Lieflier Arctica - Halfling druid of the Wizened Aspen Grove of Karana of the 35th Equinox
