 allow casters more offensive mana to be used on NUKE or DOTS.  This would over balance the Raid situation and VI won't allow that.   I can guarantee you that IF Verant would to cave into the winning of the casters wanting super immune pets, VI would inturn NERF that with either lowering the pet mob limit, or change the data on mobs to make then harder to kill.  IF you fail to see that you are stupid then I give you credit for.   <P>WHY in the hell do you think VI made so many mobs in LUCLIN tougher to solo then there cousin mobs of equal level in the older zones.  I was just in Skyfire today and tried out one of the NEW mobs to the zone, Nightshade Drake? (name could be a little off) and it was 100% immune to snare and roots.  Speed can not be changed is the message you'll get.  It is VI's vision that they want to promote more GROUPS of pc's.... not soloing or pet groups....
